replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"點解唔屌返佢而幫佢按摩呢？？？？<br />\n<br />\n同埋有時唔想同人嘈，真係唯有退讓。<br />\n<br />\n我睇心情時嘈時退"},{"pid":"81eb8c08865f23ae6edea9e1e9a28ebccdfef061","tid":400851,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:39:26.000Z","msg":"J咗樓住隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ec29ccc0efcceae23eec01e561f4f1c4d59d49","tid":400851,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:52:16.000Z","msg":"隻手咁靚<br />\n對腳都一定好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550c4e4299b0db59582c4736744e1c55eadd58b5","tid":400851,"uid":147194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"點解唔同佢講既?"},{"pid":"1e0cfa4b56eadc60c3466151b817e985a13ce41a","tid":400851,"uid":6776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出聲叫佢唔好捱落黎，problem solved <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbca85d9e49f261e0b1e59e05b8b8386413ece9c","tid":400851,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"出聲屌啦<br />\n屌柒廢老人人有責"},{"pid":"b1964e26c92a74727e648ad3608e063a31a3caaa","tid":400851,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:59:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出聲叫佢唔好捱落黎，problem solved <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「咩呀，乜條柱係你咖，我鍾意捱落黎關你撚事呀？」<br />\n<br />\n咁樣點好？"},{"pid":"08f58335ba84127cc10544c7ec8edb4daa319f0f","tid":400851,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:00:35.000Z","msg":"樓主隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢應該突登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b993ae5c5575641b90ac26caa2080c82d73a5c50","tid":400851,"uid":146917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出聲叫佢唔好捱落黎，problem solved <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「咩呀，乜條柱係你咖，我鍾意捱落黎關你撚事呀？」<br />\n<br />\n咁樣點好？</blockquote><br />\n等佢轉車企係門口位，臨閂埋門一下撞佢出去"},{"pid":"cd61198b3a0005c38ec9c65c90c562b6288311ed","tid":400851,"uid":143945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出聲叫佢唔好捱落黎，problem solved <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「咩呀，乜條柱係你咖，我鍾意捱落黎關你撚事呀？」<br />\n<br />\n咁樣點好？</blockquote><br />\n較好角度扶住吊係到嘅扶手<br />\n用你手肘對住佢個柒頭，架車一chok就可以批落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad922286dc0b3171f7bbe6a3469f85d4daa40b1","tid":400851,"uid":6955,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:13:54.000Z","msg":"好想用樓主隻手幫我打飛機"},{"pid":"f1bdff9553439b5b8b18b5810774d3871a200d2a","tid":400851,"uid":32074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出聲叫佢唔好捱落黎，problem solved <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「咩呀，乜條柱係你咖，我鍾意捱落黎關你撚事呀？」<br />\n<br />\n咁樣點好？</blockquote><br />\n撞開佢 佢問你做咩既時候答返佢 條柱你買左啊？ 我鐘意企呢邊關你撚事啊"},{"pid":"060978bb7cd7dbd8a79ba60e79ffe1beecc36dc2","tid":400851,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:16:51.000Z","msg":"鳳眼拳"},{"pid":"16ae6c161da985bcdb4b7699aa1d288ac4879b62","tid":400851,"uid":34069,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"我首先會好客氣咁同佢講唔好意思我可唔可以唔好阻住我扶手，如果佢好撚串/唔合作，我一定大大聲咁屌佢，事實係佢錯"},{"pid":"8dede929368505f679818a3b0bcccc9b1981a9b0","tid":400851,"uid":2936,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"好心你哋唔好用埋啲不痛不養嘅方法<br />\n對住呢啲人 開聲屌<br />\n你唔鍾意屌嘅 就理直氣壯咁同佢講<br />\n<br />\n道理喺你嗰邊 何需做啲陰濕手段？<br />\n連出聲屌都唔識？<br />\n<br />\n你話你屌鳩佢 影返張佢落慌而逃嘅相上嚟<br />\n我哋大家圍吓爐嘅 冇問題呀<br />\n<br />\n你乜柒都冇講 影相上嚟 個廢老唔會上連登睇<br />\n咁做對成件事冇幫助 佢都係繼續挨住條柱"},{"pid":"360f09a0408f5bc4d14a6f73a5f0bf4ae82a080a","tid":400851,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你班廢老點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/205602_30a7563e0ed200f47c072d957386d3d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F205602_30a7563e0ed200f47c072d957386d3d9.jpg&h=4d5f2ebc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好笑呀依個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4250663a66dfead74fd862f1e142541a50f71470","tid":400851,"uid":141442,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好心你哋唔好用埋啲不痛不養嘅方法<br />\n對住呢啲人 開聲屌<br />\n你唔鍾意屌嘅 就理直氣壯咁同佢講<br />\n<br />\n道理喺你嗰邊 何需做啲陰濕手段？<br />\n連出聲屌都唔識？<br />\n<br />\n你話你屌鳩佢 影返張佢落慌而逃嘅相上嚟<br />\n我哋大家圍吓爐嘅 冇問題呀<br />\n<br />\n你乜柒都冇講 影相上嚟 個廢老唔會上連登睇<br />\n咁做對成件事冇幫助 佢都係繼續挨住條柱</blockquote><br />\n就係因為我唔夠膽出聲，死毒撚一個，先po上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌左佢我就唔會po上連登啦"},{"pid":"808fa307eafab5fb64b02d7a21f187bb02dc6017","tid":400851,"uid":84381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"試過有大陸呀嬸胸壓我對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想嘔"},{"pid":"b4df9723fcb71393705bc053f7de76eda7b428ef","tid":400851,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T06:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好心你哋唔好用埋啲不痛不養嘅方法<br />\n對住呢啲人 開聲屌<br />\n你唔鍾意屌嘅 就理直氣壯咁同佢講<br />\n<br />\n道理喺你嗰邊 何需做啲陰濕手段？<br />\n連出聲屌都唔識？<br />\n<br />\n你話你屌鳩佢 影返張佢落慌而逃嘅相上嚟<br />\